        <dbl>
1       0.641
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# base R:
cor(gapm$life_expectancy_years_2011, 
    gapm$female_literacy_rate_2011,
    use =  "complete.obs")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
